Legendary Golem - Regice ‚Üí Legendary Golem of Regal Ice

1991507 ⋅ DB ⋅ EXU

‚úÖ ‚ùå ü™ì üíº üóëÔ∏è

Legendary Golem - Regice

name: Legendary Golem - Regice
level: 10
effect

  • You can only control 1 "Legendary Golem - Regice". You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by discarding 1 card or by controlling a "Legendary Golem" card. Once per Chain, when your opponent activates the effect of a monster whose ATK is less than or equal to this card's DEF (including during the Damage Step) (Quick Effect): You can make this card lose 500 DEF, and if you do, this card is unaffected by monster effects for the rest of this Chain. The first time each "Legendary Golem" card you control would be destroyed by card effect each turn, it is not destroyed.

‚û°Ô∏è

Legendary Golem of Regal Ice

name: Legendary Golem of Regal Ice
level: 9
effect

  • You can only control 1 "Legendary Golem of Regal Ice". You can Special Summon this card (from your hand) by discarding 1 card or by controlling a "Legendary Golem" card. Once per Chain (Quick Effect): You can make this card unaffected by the activated effects of monsters with ATK less than or equal to this card's DEF for the rest of this Chain, and if you do, reduce this card's DEF by 500 once this Chain has finished resolving. The first time each "Legendary Golem" card you control would be destroyed by card effect each turn, you can reduce the ATK of 1 "Legendary Golem" monster in its column by 500 instead.

  • ‚óè Monster that was on the field for 2 or more End Phases, or a WATER monster: Special Summon 1 "Legendary Golem - Regice" from your Deck.
  • You can only control 1 "Legendary Golems - Awaken!".

Legendary Golem's Sealed Chamber

name: Legendary Golem's Sealed Chamber
effect

  • ‚óèWinged Beast monster in your center Main Monster Zone, or a LIGHT monster: Special Summon 1 "Legendary Golem of Regal Steel" from your Deck.
  • ‚óè Monster that was on the field while the turn count moved forward twice or more, or a WATER monster: Special Summon 1 "Legendary Golem of Regal Ice" from your Deck
  • You can only control 1 "Legendary Golem's Sealed Chamber".

Legendary Golem's Crush Grip

name: Legendary Golem's Crush Grip
card_type: Trap
type: Continuous
effect

  • If a "Legendary Golem" monster you control destroys a monster by battle: You can change its battle position, and if you do, banish cards from the top of your opponent's Deck face-down, up to the number of "Legendary Golem" cards you control. You can discard 1 card, then target 1 card on the field; destroy it, but if you do not control "Legendary Golem Crafter -Regigigas", you must discard a "Legendary Golem" card to activate this effect. You can only use each effect of "Legendary Golem's Crush Grip" once per turn.

‚û°Ô∏è

Crush Grip

name: Crush Grip
card_type: Spell
type: Quick-Play
effect

  • Activate 1 of the following effects.
  • ‚óè Add 1 "Legendary Golem" card from your Deck to your hand, then you can move the turn count forward by 1 for each different Attribute among "Legendary Golem" monsters you control.
  • ‚óè If you control a "Legendary Golem" monster: Target 1 card on the field; destroy it, then if you control "Continent Mover, the Legendary Golem Crafter" you can banish 1 card from the top of your opponent's Deck face-down for every 2000 LP they have.
  • You can only activate 1 "Crush Grip" per turn.
